Installation
============

You can download a pre-compiled package for your CPU's architecture and OS from: <https://github.com/sparky-game/carbon/releases>.

However, if you prefer to build it from source, you can do it with:
```
cc src/make.c -o make
./make
```

After obtaining either way the package file, you can install it to your desired location with:
```
export PREFIX="~/.local/opt/carbon/"
mkdir -p $PREFIX
tar -xvf carbon-*.tgz -C $PREFIX
```
